system configuration information

flat_mib_tree.name: sysConfName
flat_mib_tree.description: Configured name of the AirPort Base Station.

flat_mib_tree.name: sysConfContact
flat_mib_tree.description: Configured name of the contact for the AirPort Base Station.

flat_mib_tree.name: sysConfLocation
flat_mib_tree.description: Configured name of where the AirPort Base Station is located.

flat_mib_tree.name: sysConfUptime
flat_mib_tree.description: Length of time, in seconds, the AirPort Base Station has been running.

flat_mib_tree.name: sysConfFirmwareVersion
flat_mib_tree.description: Current firmware revision running on the AirPort Base Station.

information about wireless clients

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessNumber
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of wireless clients associated with this AP.

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessClientsTable
flat_mib_tree.description: A list of wireless clients.

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessClient
flat_mib_tree.description: A wireless client entry containing information about the client.

indexes.name: wirelessPhysAddress
indexes.description: The MAC address of the wireless client.

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessPhysAddress
flat_mib_tree.description: The MAC address of the wireless client.

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessType
flat_mib_tree.description: The type of wireless client node.

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessDataRates
flat_mib_tree.description: The data rates available for the wireless client.

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessTimeAssociated
flat_mib_tree.description: The time that this wireless client associated.

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessLastRefreshTime
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of seconds since the client reported its statistics to the AirPort Base Station (-1 if never refreshed or not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessStrength
flat_mib_tree.description: The signal strength reported by the wireless client (-1 if not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessNoise
flat_mib_tree.description: The noise reported by the wireless client (-1 if not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessRate
flat_mib_tree.description: The rate reported by the wireless client (-1 if not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessNumRX
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of packets received reported by the wireless client (-1 if not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessNumTX
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of packets transmitted reported by this wireless client (-1 if not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessNumRXErrors
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of errors encountered receiving packets reported by this wireless client (-1 if not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: wirelessNumTXErrors
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of errors encountered transmitting packets reported by this wireless client (-1 if not supported).

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpServer
flat_mib_tree.description: information about DHCP server

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpNumber
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of DHCP clients served by the AirPort base station.

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpClientsTable
flat_mib_tree.description: A list of DHCP clients.

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpClient
flat_mib_tree.description: A DHCP client entry containing information about the client.

indexes.name: dhcpPhysAddress
indexes.description: The MAC address of the DHCP client.

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpPhysAddress
flat_mib_tree.description: The MAC address of the DHCP client.

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpIpAddress
flat_mib_tree.description: The IP address of the DHCP client.

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpClientID
flat_mib_tree.description: The DHCP client ID of the DHCP client.

flat_mib_tree.name: dhcpLeaseTime
flat_mib_tree.description: The lease time for the DHCP client.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaces
flat_mib_tree.description: physical interfaces table

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceCount
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of physical interfaces on the AirPort Base Station.  This is different than the number of IP interfaces, as reported by the system MIBs, as the AirPort's bridge typically multiplexes two or more interfaces.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfacesTable
flat_mib_tree.description: List of physical interfaces on the AirPort Base Station.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterface
flat_mib_tree.description: Entry containing data about the physical interface on the AirPort Base Station.

indexes.name: physicalInterfaceIndex
indexes.description: A unique value for each physical interface.  Its value ranges between 1 and the value of physicalInterfaceCount.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceIndex
flat_mib_tree.description: A unique value for each physical interface.  Its value ranges between 1 and the value of physicalInterfaceCount.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceName
flat_mib_tree.description: The name of the physical interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceUnit
flat_mib_tree.description: The unit number of the physical interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceSpeed
flat_mib_tree.description: The speed, in bits per second, of the interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceState
flat_mib_tree.description: The status of this interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceDuplex
flat_mib_tree.description: The duplex-state of this interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceNumTX
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of packets transmitted on this interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceNumRX
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of packets received on this interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceNumTXError
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of errors during transmission on this interface.

flat_mib_tree.name: physicalInterfaceNumRXError
flat_mib_tree.description: The number of errors during reception on this interface.
